cff-version: 1.2.0
title: >-
  From Model Uncertainty to Human Attention: Localization-Aware Visual
  Cues for Scalable Annotation Review
message: >-
  If you use this software or the re-annotated ground truth, please cite
  the paper using the metadata below.
